mixin tourItem(rowClass, colClass, inc)
    ul.tour__items(class!=rowClass)
        each item, i in tourItem
            if i < inc
                li.tour__item(class!=colClass)
                    .tour__thumb.ratio-container
                        img(src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==", alt=""
                            data-sizes="auto"
                            data-src=`./images/pic/${item.image}.jpg`
                            data-srcset=`./images/pic/${item.image}.jpg 300w,
                            ./images/pic/${item.image}.jpg 600w,
                            ./images/pic/${item.image}.jpg 900w`).lazyload.blur-up
                        .tour__icon 
                            +icon(`${item.icon}`,{cls: "tour__svg"})
                    .tour__title!=item.title
                    .tour__subtitle 
                        | Вероятностная логика, конечно, транспонирует онтологический гедонизм. 
                    .tour__btn 
                        a(href="assosation-inner.html").tour__link.btn.btn-white
                            | Подробнее

